'''''Place of Weeping''''' (ikinamico nka '''Afrika - Land der Hoffnung''' ), ni filime y'ikinamico yo [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afrika yepfo]] yasohotse muri 1986 yayobowe na Darrell Roodt ikanakorwa na Anant Singh muri Place of Weeping Productions.   Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo James Whyle, Gcina Mhlophe na Charles Comyn mu bakinnyi ba mbere mu gihe Norman Coombes, Michelle du Toit, Kerneels Coertzen na Patrick Shai bagize uruhare runini.   Iyi filime isobanura mu buryo burambuye ku matsinda y’imico myinshi yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'epfo n’uburyo [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] yepfo yaguye kubera ibikorwa by’abanyafurika yepfo n’amakimbirane mu butegetsi bukandamiza [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] yepfo.  

Iyi niyo shusho yambere yo kurwanya ivanguramoko yakozwe muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo. Filime yagaragaye bwa mbere ku ya 5 Ukuboza 1986. Filime yakiriwe neza nabayireba 

